# Cursor Rules for Portfolio Project

## Tech Stack

- SolidJS with @solidjs/start (file-based routing)
- TailwindCSS with custom accent colors (camel theme: accent-300 to accent-600)
- Vinxi bundler
- TypeScript strict mode
- Path alias: ~/src/\*

## Code Style

- Framework imports first, then type imports, then local components/libs
- Use `type` imports for TypeScript types
- Default exports for pages/components, named exports for utilities
- Props: explicit interface/type definitions like `{ photos: Photo[] }`
- SolidJS: createSignal, createMemo, createResource patterns
- Event handlers: arrow functions with explicit types `(e: KeyboardEvent)`
- Always check `typeof window !== 'undefined'` for client-only code
- Include ARIA labels and keyboard navigation
- Use lazy loading, draggable={false}, prevent context menus on images

## Commands

- Dev: `pnpm dev`
- Build: `pnpm build` (includes photo manifest generation)
- No test framework - use TypeScript compiler for validation

## File Structure

- Components in ~/components/
- Routes in ~/routes/ (file-based routing)
- Utilities in ~/lib/
- Types defined inline or in component files
